            <msItem xml:id="a1" n="1">
              <locus from="1a"/>
              <title xml:lang="en">The Psalms, according to the Peshitta version</title>
              <finalRubric xml:lang="syr">ܫ̣ܠܡ ܠܡ̣ܟܬܒ. ܬܫ̈ܒܚܬܐ. ܕܕܘܝܕ. ܕܗ̇ܘܝܢ. ܒܡܢܝ̣ܢܐ. ܡܐܐ ܘܚ̈ܡܫܝܢ
                ܦ̄ܬ : ܕܝܢ ܗ̇ܘܝܢ. ܐܪ̈ܒܥܐ: ܐܠܦ̈ܝܢ. ܘܬܡ̈ܢܡܐܐ. ܘ̈ܬܠܬܝܢ ܘܬܪ̈ܝܢ.<locus from="61b"/>
              </finalRubric>
              <note>The missing portions are: Ps. i. 1—xxxv. 9, and xlvii. 1—xlix. 8. The headings
                are different from these in Lee's edition. </note>
              <note>The ܡܪ̈ܡܝܬܐ and ܫܘ̈ܒܚܐ are marked by a later hand on the margins.</note>
            </msItem>
